{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-14702/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-14702"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["1:47:02"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["medium shot"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["low"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["interior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["mobile, handheld"]}},{"label":{"none":["Composition"]},"value":{"none":["two shot"]}}],"summary":{"none":["A man and woman stare at each other angrily."]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14702/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-14702","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14702/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-14702"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14702/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14702/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14702/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14702/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14702/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14702/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14702/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14702/canvas/1/6d2a8d7e-c4b9-40ad-bf6b-98ce36d0671c","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-07-02T19:54:21.576Z","creator":"Ada ","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>On their first date, Alma challenges Reynolds to a staring contest and elsewhere claims that she can stand longer than anyone else. Here, she makes good on her promises. She meets Reynolds’s gaze without backing down and stands nearly motionless, firm in her resolve to stand up to her husband and his demanding ways.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14702/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:1330.4976114649678,96.01015127388516,323.12400477707024,412.9806926751592"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14702/canvas/1/2202d16f-d539-4862-afb0-f646397fd94b","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-07-02T19:54:42.643Z","creator":"Ada ","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Another wordless conversation (confrontation) between characters. In <em>Phantom Thread</em>, PTA is unafraid to let his characters communicate and convey their emotions and intentions in this way.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14702/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:455.9668590764328,18.258857484076344,320.0472730891717,391.56449044585986"}}}]}]}]}